<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title><% title%></title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "bootstrap.min", :media => "all" %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "bootstrap.min.responsive", :media => "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
</head>
<body>

<div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
      <div class="navbar-inner">
        <div class="container">
          <a class="btn btn-navbar" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".nav-collapse">

            <span class="i-bar"></span>
            <span class="i-bar"></span>
            <span class="i-bar"></span>
          </a>
		  <%= link_to logo, root_path, :class => "brand" %>
          <div class="nav-collapse">
            <% if signed_in? %>
				<ul class="nav">
					<li><%= link_to "Профиль", current_user %></li>
					<li><%= link_to "Настройки", edit_user_path(current_user) %></li>
					<li><a href="#">Награды</a></li>
					<li><%= link_to "Выйти", signout_path, :method => :delete %></li>
				</ul>
			<% end %>
          </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">

      <!-- Main hero unit for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
      <div class="hero-unit">
	  
		<div class="row-fluid show-grid">
		<%= controller_name %><br />
		<%= action_name %><br />
		<%= session[:user_id] %>
			<%= yield %>
			<% if !signed_in? %>
				<form id="authform" action="<%= url_for(:action => 'new', :controller => 'sessions') %>" method="post" accept-charset="UTF-8">
					<input type="hidden" name="authenticity_token" value="<%= form_authenticity_token %>" />
						<% params.each do |param, value| %>
					<% end %>
					<input type="submit" value="Войти" />
				</form>
				<script type="text/javascript">
					$().ready(function(){
						#$("#authform").submit();
					});
				</script>
			<% end %>
<% if Rails.env.production? %>
        <%#= debug(cookies) %>
<% end %>
		</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Example row of columns -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span4">
          <h2>Новые запросы</h2>
           <p>Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus. Etiam porta sem malesuada magna mollis euismod. Donec sed odio dui. </p>
          <p><a class="btn" href="#">View details &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="span4">
          <h2>Новые ответы</h2>
           <p>Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus. Etiam porta sem malesuada magna mollis euismod. Donec sed odio dui. </p>
          <p><a class="btn" href="#">View details &raquo;</a></p>
       </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h2>Heading</h2>

          <p>Donec sed odio dui. Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus.</p>
          <p><a class="btn" href="#">View details &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <footer>
        <p>&copy; Awesome Studio 2012</p>

      </footer>

    </div> <!-- /container -->

</body>
</html>
